provide specific functionality
assist kumu in improving the kumu Services and developing new services and features
fulfill, distribute and process returns of products,  orders or contest prizes
conduct data analysis and report creation
process payments
prevent, detect, and investigate fraud or other prohibited actions
BUSINESS PARTNERS
Campaigns, Contests and Gaming Tournament partners.
